Joan Lowell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joan_Lowell 0 Helen Joan Lowell (November 23, 1902 – November 7, 1967) was a movie actress of the silent film era from Berkeley, California. Lowell published a sensational autobiography, Cradle of the Deep, in 1929, which turned out to be a pure fabrication.
